ktorrent: KTorrent - A BitTorrent client for KDE
ktorrent:
ktorrent: KTorrent is a BitTorrent program for KDE.  It allows a user to
ktorrent: download torrent files and includes features such as: upload and
ktorrent: download speed capping, Internet searching, UDP Trackers, port
ktorrent: forwarding with UPnP, IP blocking, importing of partially or fully
ktorrent: downloaded files, distributed hash tables, protocol encryption,
ktorrent: bandwidth scheduling, and many more features. Now it comes with
ktorrent: slick IDEAl GUI interface.
ktorrent:
ktorrent: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov (gdsotirov@dir.bg)
